public interface LccIUiComponent
extends java.lang.Iterable<LccIUiComponent>

Components that represent Tags on HTML. Like inputtext, div, select... It use Composite Pattern, permiting create components bigger then one tag, like tables and a whole page. Composites must implements LccIUiComposite

Author:
Lucas Gonçalves
